OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783947031
OL,3,CMajor chemical plant proposes closure
OL,5,FA chemicals manufacturer has announced
OL,6,Fplans to consult staff over a proposal
OL,7,Fto cease operations in Lancashire,
OL,8,Fputting almost 200 jobs at risk.
OL,10,FAGC Chemicals Europe, Ltd. based at
OL,11,FHillhouse Technology Enterprise Zone
OL,12,Fin Thornton-Cleveleys, say they face
OL,13,F"significant financial and operational
OL,14,Fchallenges.", and have been generating
OL,15,Fa loss for the past four years.
OL,17,FThe company has said the closure is
OL,18,Fonly a proposal and no final decision
OL,19,Fhas been made yet.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
