OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783947031
OL,3,CMajor chemical plant proposes closure
OL,5,FThe consultation process is expected
OL,6,Fto take at least 45 days, and all
OL,7,Froles at the site could be affected -
OL,8,Fincluding 190 members of staff and 18
OL,9,Fagency workers. It's suggested that
OL,10,Fproduction could finish by the end of
OL,11,F2026.
OL,13,FAGC Chemicals Europe is part of the
OL,14,FAGC Group, one of the world's biggest
OL,15,Fmanufacturers of glass, chemicals,
OL,16,Felectronics, and ceramics.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
