OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783947032
OL,3,CMajor chemical plant proposes closure
OL,5,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,6,F"AGC Chemicals Europe, Ltd. has today
OL,7,Fannounced that it is consulting with
OL,8,Femployees and their representatives
OL,9,Fabout a proposal to cease operations
OL,10,Fat its manufacturing plant at the
OL,11,FHillhouse Technology Enterprise Zone
OL,12,Fin Thornton Cleveleys, Lancashire. All
OL,13,Froles at the site are affected.
OL,15,F"This is a proposal only and no final
OL,16,Fdecision has been made.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783947032
OL,3,CMajor chemical plant proposes closure
OL,5,F"This proposal has been made because
OL,6,Fthe site has experienced significant
OL,7,Ffinancial and operational challenges,
OL,8,Fgenerating a loss for the past four
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,F"Despite continued investment from AGC
OL,12,FInc. and the hard work of Hillhouse
OL,13,Femployees, the situation is no longer
OL,14,Fsustainable in the context of a
OL,15,Fvolatile and competitive market.
OL,17,F"Our immediate focus is the people who
OL,18,Fare affected, and to begin a
OL,19,Fmeaningful consultation process.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783947032
OL,3,CMajor chemical plant proposes closure
OL,5,F"The consultation is expected to take
OL,6,Fat least 45 days. AGC Chemicals
OL,7,FEurope, Ltd. will work closely with
OL,8,Funions and employee representatives
OL,9,Fwith a view to seeking their agreement
OL,10,Fon various matters, including how we
OL,11,Fmight avoid or reduce dismissals and
OL,12,Fmitigate the impact for employees.
OL,14,FEarlier this year, Wyre Council and
OL,15,Fthe Environment Agency closed two
OL,16,Fallotments in Thornton-Cleveleys as
OL,17,Fpart of an investigation into
OL,18,Fpotential historic contamination that
OL,19,Fmay increase the risk of cancer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
