PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783947032
OL,3,CMajor chemical plant proposes closure
OL,5,FA multi-agency investigation was
OL,6,Flaunched in 2024 to examine potential
OL,7,Fhistoric contamination by the chemical
OL,8,Fperfluorooctanoic acid (PFOA) from
OL,9,Fpart of the former ICI site, now
OL,10,Foperated by AGC Chemicals.
OL,12,FIn a statement provided in March, the
OL,13,Fgroup said: "AGC Chemicals Europe,
OL,14,FLtd. has not yet been provided with
OL,15,Fthe details of the Environment Agency
OL,16,FInterpretive report relating to the
OL,17,Fallotment site.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783947032
OL,3,CMajor chemical plant proposes closure
OL,5,F"However, our highest priority is
OL,6,Fsupporting the community that we live
OL,7,Fand work in, which is why we are
OL,8,Fworking alongside the multi-agency
OL,9,Finvestigation and conducting our own
OL,10,Fvoluntary investigation on the section
OL,11,Fof land at the former ICI site that we
OL,12,Foccupy."
OL,14,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,15,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,16,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,17,Four region.
